buildCommand:
mkdir -p $out/nar

cat $NIX_ATTRS_JSON_FILE > $out/attrs.json

python /nix/store/739lvap0p329mpahi1hicn6p0b3say1w-make-binary-cache.py

# These directories must exist, or Nix might try to create them in LocalBinaryCacheStore::init(),
# which fails if mounted read-only
mkdir $out/realisations
mkdir $out/debuginfo
mkdir $out/log
name: binary-cache
